data.description: Updated 4 bedroom cape code on almost an acre of land in Boardman. Easy access to schools, shopping, restaurants and freeways but far enough away to avoid the hustle and bustle. Scenic lot has a pond with water feature, two car garage with loft area and an enclosed patio off the back of the house. Inside you'll find an updated eat-in kitchen with almost new appliances, living room and two bedrooms on the first floor with full bathroom. Upstairs are two more bedrooms built-ins. There have been lots of updates to this home so ask you REALTOR for the complete list.
